headline: State Street (STT): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q2 Earnings?
summary: State Street has had an impressive run over the past six months as its shares have beaten the S&P 500 by 9.3%. The stock now trades at $111.70, marking a 26.8% gain. This performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
